properties.name: The Riding Dead
properties.description:
Now, any time is a good time for a zombie apocalypse, it is true. But what time is more appropriate than this, the spookiest time of year? No time, we say! So, this week, we stagger and shuffle around some of the undead's favorite haunts, like open fields and shopping malls and maybe a few pointless dead ends. None shall be safe from our relentless search for brainzz (and adventure!).
